# Trivy ignore list — scoped, documented, and time-bound.
#
# These are OpenSSL/libssl3 CVEs in the Debian 12 base layer of the
# gcr.io/distroless/nodejs22-debian12 image. Debian has published fixes, but the
# upstream distroless base had not yet been rebuilt with them at release time,
# so `ignore-unfixed: true` does not skip them.
#
# Context / risk acceptance: the app serves plain HTTP inside the cluster; all
# TLS is terminated at Cloudflare's edge and the cloudflared tunnel, so this
# OpenSSL is not on the request path. Exposure is negligible for this workload.
#
# ACTION: remove these lines once the distroless base is rebuilt (re-run the
# monthly image rebuild); the scan will then pass without exceptions.
# Reviewed: 2026-07-03
